item.title: How do you change where a tele spell takes you?
item.dc:creator: @d_man103456 d man103456
item.description:
@d_man103456 wrote:

it will either be in your clickingMost class or client class, find where the teleport takes you and change the x and y coords to where you want the teleport to take you. If the teleport does not take you anywhere then you will case to find the case for the button and create a case for it.
